Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放輕鬆點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.13,0:03:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然能來幫忙這點很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.24,0:03:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣下去可真讓人擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 真是好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是日日乃的親戚詩緒小朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.57,0:04:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大學裡的朋友小詩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小的真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人怎麼回事...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.99,0:04:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.29,0:04:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小詩就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很在意!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是挺好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 詩緒小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在幫忙做事 別妨礙我!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「來者何人」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.25,0:05:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼好像只對我態度很差?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.64,0:05:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的待會我來做 你可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著慢著慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.42,0:05:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用那麼著急的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得去學習...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(300,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得用{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}把「空戰奇兵」的戰鬥給通關才行...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.79,0:05:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習的話一會再做也行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我來看你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是給你隨便逗著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  我們好好相處嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.60,0:05:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我請你吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你 特製巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.54,0:05:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.44,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看上去很幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子真讓人羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是稍不留神這裡就胖起來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等回過神來時體重早已闖進無可挽救的領域了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣的事情也偶爾會有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來詩緒好像也稍微胖了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是新推出的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能試吃下然後告訴我你的感想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 中午想吃什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.63,0:06:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你有印象呢 詩緒小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是長身體的時候 不用在意對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.58,0:06:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不準哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以為自己是小孩子就大吃特吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:06:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體重可是會一直線上升的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 再吃一碟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.12,0:07:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小詩你真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.41,0:07:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想拜託你試吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.05,0:07:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連爸爸都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 我把你說的那個蛋糕買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.00,0:07:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間的事真是難以預料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到枸雅君會變成在日日乃家裡吃閒飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒別的事的話我就...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這冷淡的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.35,0:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要說的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.29,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然發生了很不得了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好在結果還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:07:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是你說還企圖著別的什麼機會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是要遭報應的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.47,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.44,0:08:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君你啊 現在全研討會的男生都很嫉妒你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饒了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你身邊又有這麼可愛的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也做不了什麼奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人好像聊得很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.71,0:08:43.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天沒有課 我們一起出去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枸雅君哪裡也沒帶你去過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是必須得訓練...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}也一起帶上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.79,0:09:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是詩緒不在的話店裡的營業額...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.92,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(480,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了進行操縱{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}的訓練必須找個開放的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不會被人發現的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(610,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來雖然不知道{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}的內部構造是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海水裡也沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你沒想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.26,0:09:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 普通的水是沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該就沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海底好像沉了各種各種的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(725,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 你能通過{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}看到海底啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:10:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但因為海水很渾濁只能看到前方一點點的範圍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是這樣轉來轉去也訓練不出什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.15,0:10:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要試著挖個東西看看?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 媽媽看到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爆炸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.23,0:10:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平還不來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說了打工結束之後會聯繫我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不我先發個簡訊過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想要手機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:10:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母不給你買嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:05.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1015,650)\c&H1414FF&}ククリ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過如果是為了保護你的話 反正有{\c&H1414FF&}玖吼理{\r}在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你有發簡訊的對象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是每天都能見面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.79,0:11:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間拖得太久了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.06,0:11:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日日乃同學打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.74,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.17,0:12:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來剛才排隊的時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.31,0:12:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都擺出一副厭惡的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上相當臭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.85,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是惹老子不爽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把那些個一臉幸福的小鬼給這樣...宰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回村子裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對好久不見的兒時玩伴所說的話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一直沒來牢裡看我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再...繼續鬧事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算我拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能回村子裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你像這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低下頭來的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在傷害我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一起在卡拉OK包廂裡的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咧 要不要對她下手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.61,0:13:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別畏首畏尾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別當一切都沒發生過一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是真正的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時開始你我就已經走上同一條道路了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.59,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.14,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日日乃同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我還沒到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.50,0:14:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿幾真叫人傷腦筋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.49,0:14:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾司朗...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.46,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個麻煩人物就交給我們處理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 阿幾那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.97,0:14:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑得比誰都快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.27,0:14:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 勾司朗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.81,0:14:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.47,0:14:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捂住你的耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也別說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.28,0:15:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非你想與我為敵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是趕不上時間了 讓我們先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那過會也不能與我們匯合了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去吃待會能讓枸雅君羡慕的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.36,0:15:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸緒...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.98,0:16:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.66,0:16:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第二次救了人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.51,0:16:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次連我也被你救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進步了不少嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人欽佩啊 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:16:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.51,0:17:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾司朗居然來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是麻煩的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙真叫人不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匡平
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我們不知犧牲了多少無可替代的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而打開了地獄之門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你卻裝作若無其事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅僅只有你享樂其中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也太自私自利了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.01,0:17:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好相反吧 阿幾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.68,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為我犧牲了無可替代的東西...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.31,0:18:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勾司朗...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西無誤 謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那報酬還是匯到以前的帳戶裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想下次的委託應該是在下周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我稍有耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空張的爸爸是員警吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.13,0:18:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是他知道了本該遵紀守法的女兒卻做些非法打工的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你爸爸會怎麼想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.05,0:18:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.04,0:18:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那笨蛋老爸與世間一般的常識是無緣的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就別妄想為了「以防萬一」 先和員警打好關係這種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有那個意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.98,0:19:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖太顯而易見了 死胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼 好臭...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然外型不同 但是不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是同一類東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在多管閒事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.00,0:20:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不出手的話你早被幹掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該就倒在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 好像逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.49,0:20:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 果然還只是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後關頭掉以輕心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撿到...好東西了呢

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.17,0:22:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神樣DOLLS 講座 擴大版
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.55,0:22:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電視機前的各位晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.31,0:22:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.05,0:22:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 玖吼理也向大家問好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.09,0:22:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比平時轉得更猛了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力氣用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.09,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.36,0:22:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然寄來了這麼多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.82,0:22:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒一個人看不了這麼多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.78,0:22:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詩緒 把神樣DOLLS的秘密偷偷地告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.45,0:22:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}只悄悄地告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}這是玖吼理的內部圖解
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}圖:詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我猜想的玖吼理的內部圖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.42,0:23:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣... 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.66,0:23:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果啟動了隱藏力量的話 會發生無法挽回的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.44,0:23:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?沒問題?基本上都說對了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.46,0:23:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛痛 玖吼理
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開放開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}只悄悄地告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}這是空守村的全景
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}建設預定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}圖:詩緒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.74,0:23:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我想像的空守村的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡會預計建成這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會好好加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為全世界最棒的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.99,0:23:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍後繼續送上神樣DOLLS講座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎖定頻道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.19,0:23:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又見面了呢 神樣DOLLS 講座
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.96,0:23:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要為你介紹...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能清楚地看出每個人身高的不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玖吼理也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.91,0:23:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個人都比詩緒高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.25,0:23:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.98,0:23:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬請期待
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.71,0:23:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣都一定要看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.75,0:00:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

